---
title: Double Sweet Chilli Beef Rump & Corn Veggie Toss with Asian Mayo & Crispy Shallots
description: A rich sauce can give a wealth of flavour to tender beef rump. Take this soy sauce and mayo combination, it’s loaded with delicious aromas that elevate this sweet chilli beef to the next level. For a pop of gold in your veggie toss add some charred corn to the mix. We’re sure your dinner experience will be newly enriched.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6645bf512537d3c1a9bdd4d6-2e9203c6-858d2cdf.jpeg
